<sect1 id="Config.CcShape">
	<title>Concept Class Shapes</title>
	<para>It is possible to change the shape of each concept class</para>
	<para>
        <screenshot>
          <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
              <imagedata align="center" fileref="../images/Scaled/config_ccShape1.png"/>
            </imageobject>
          </mediaobject>
        </screenshot>
	</para>
	<para>Clicking on a shape in the shape column will make a drop-down list appear which contains different shapes to choose from:</para>
	<para>
        <screenshot>
          <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
              <imagedata align="center" fileref="../images/Scaled/config_ccShape2.png"/>
            </imageobject>
          </mediaobject>
        </screenshot>
	</para>
</sect1>